options.text: Scientists think that there has been life on the earth for hundreds of millions of years. However, we have not found life on any other planets yet. The earth is a planet and it goes around the sun. Seven other planets also go around the sun. None of them has an environment like that of the earth, so scientists do not think they will find life on them. The sun and its planets are called the solar system, and our solar system is a small part of a much larger group of stars and planets, called the Galaxy or the Milky Way.

content.contentDesc:
W: Look! This looks so interesting! There are dragons and frogs on it.

M: Ah, it's a great invention of ancient China.

W: Really? When was it invented?

M: In the Han Dynasty.

W: Han Dynasty? And what was it used for? For holding water or food?

M: Neither. For testing the earthquakes.

content.contentDesc: People began to use robots about two hundred years ago. At first, robots only did the same things again and again. However, modern robots are smarter. Some can solve problems by themselves because their brains are computers. They are very helpful. In the future, robots will be able to teach languages online. Some scientists believe that this will happen in twenty years. And there will be more robots everywhere. Human will have less work to do, and everyone will have more free time to relax.

subContents.content: 你的转述可以这样开始：It's sunny today...

sentencePatterns: It's sunny today, on my way home, I saw an old man walking slowly around the street corner.
Suddenly he fell down, and he passed out.
I looked around, and found a telephone box.
So I called the police at once.
I felt very proud of myself.
oralDict.contentDesc: It's sunny today. On my way home, I saw an old man walking slowly around the street corner. Suddenly he fell down, I ran to him, and he passed out. I couldn't move him. What should I do? I looked around, and found a telephone box. So I called the police at once, and they came along very soon. They sent the old man to the hospital and thanked me for my help. I said "It's my pleasure to do so, and everyone needs help." I felt very proud of myself.
